info:
Deep, intense, ruby-red;
Notes of blackberries, black currant, chocolate, dry plums and vanilla;
Good body, harmonic, balanced and persistent aftertaste
红色带紫色光泽；
浆果、黑醋栗和巧克力的香味，以及干李子和香草气息；
酒体和谐，平衡。余味悠长持久

Dark and deep purple;
Subtle aromas of chocolate, dark plums, berries, and spices. With hints of vanilla and smoke;
Medium-bodied, with lovely tannins and a long finish.
深沉的暗紫色；
巧克力、黒加仑、浆果和香料的气味，并隐含香草和烟草的味道；
酒体适中，单宁美好，余味绵长、令人愉悦

Crimson purple colour;
Blueberries, violets and cherry ripe with hints of cinnamon;
Vibrant and medium bodied, fine white pepper tannins and hints of cherry in finish. 
紫红色泽；
蓝莓，紫罗兰，成熟樱桃混杂丝丝桂皮辛香；
活跃的中度酒体，细致单宁搭配轻微白胡椒和樱桃果香，余韵绵长

Ripe gooseberry, passionfruit, fresh citrus lime and exotic herbaceous aromas;
Exciting palate with layers of juicy flavours, intensity and fullness
成熟的猕猴桃，西番莲，新鲜柑橘和异国情调的草本植物味; 
口味清爽，果味丰满多汁，余味清新明快

Bright yellow;
Aromas of pineapple and papaya, notes of apple, butter and wood, ntense tropical fruit flavors;
Medium bodied, refreshing, soft, and balanced
浅黄色；
富含木瓜、苹果和柠檬的果香，也有黄油和木材的气息；
清新、柔和、平衡，略带甜味

Intense ruby colour;
Pure, delicate aromas of ripe blackcurrants, wild strawberries and blackberries, blended with minerals, vanilla, coffee, licorice and spices.;
Outstanding balance, a firm tannic structure anbd exceptional length.
浓郁宝石红色；
干净精致的成熟黑醋栗，野草莓，黑莓果味，丝丝香草，咖啡和甘草等木味辛香；
口感平衡出众，单宁紧实，酒体浓郁，质地精美
